Class TradeTileFragment

    Observer

    public class TradeTileFragment
extends Fragment
implements Observer
    A simple Fragment subclass. Activities that contain this fragment must implement the TradeTileFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener interface to handle interaction events. Use the newInstance(java.lang.String, java.lang.String) factory method to create an instance of this fragment.
